OL,5, Oscar-winning director Paul Haggis has 
OL,6, been arrested in southern Italy on     
OL,7, suspicion of aggravated sexual assault,
OL,8, Italian news agencies have reported.   
OL,10,FBrindisi prosecutors said he was also  
OL,11,Faccused of "aggravated personal injury 
OL,12,Fand crimes committed to the prejudice  
OL,13,Fof a young foreign woman".             
OL,15,FThe ANSA and AGI agencies also report  
OL,16,FMr Haggis has denied the allegations   
OL,17,Fvia his lawyer, Michele Laforgia.      
OL,19,FThe BBC has contacted Mr Haggis's      
OL,20,Frepresentatives and the prosecutors.   
